<doc id="232124" wikidata="Q836658" url="?curid=232124" title="Kobe Electric Railway">
<text>, often called , is a Japanese private railway company in Kobe and surrounding cities. It is a subsidiary of Hankyu Hanshin Toho Group.

==Lines==
*Arima Line (Minatogawa - Arima Onsen)
*Sanda Line (Arimaguchi - Sanda)
*Kōen-Toshi Line (Yokoyama - Woody Town Chuo)
*Ao Line (Suzurandai - Ao)
*Kobe Kosoku Line (Shinkaichi - Minatogawa) - Kobe Rapid Transit Railway owns the tracks of the line as the &quot;Namboku Line&quot;. Shintetsu operates trains on the line.
